e":"2019-07-26T06:13:53.000Z","msg":"小小建議<br />\n去元西同朗西嘅天橋一定要守住<br />\n<br />\n聽日如果有事要走佬 千祈唔好上輕鐵，會開唔到車然後困死左<br />\n<br />\n咁多共享單車 可以揾人排好哂比埋錢走佬用<br />\n<br />\n好多鋪頭都係鄉黑開嘅 唔好見係鋪頭就衝入去 有機會送死 走入商場會好啲"},{"pid":"29d55de656d8b80577a333232d85d7a2e1330807","tid":1366921,"uid":76368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，畫得好用心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbbfd01e091f25cfa27bbf0c0ee8fabbbd41579","tid":1366921,"uid":63892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"張圖畫得好趣緻<br />\n作為元朗人未用過呢個角度去睇元朗<br />\n咁樣畫十字黎分，有趣有趣👍"},{"pid":"5a9474145c6d6e963ae9d4d079144263bccbce68","tid":1366921,"uid":267074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"722dc03c0ee21e85be408a27106237e310bdc9c6","tid":1366921,"uid":109414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a533ceb3a34dd7a220410e2465cbb3fd929890b5","tid":1366921,"uid":157220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}